data.name: label2.Text
data.value: By pressing "Finish" button you will unregister Fb2ePub shell extension. Meaning the Fb2 to ePub conversion on the right mouse click will no longer be available on your computer. If that's what you want to do, go ahead and press "Finish". If you are got here by mistake or reconsidered - use "Back" button to return to previous wizard dialog.

data.name: label1.Text
data.value: Please select operation you wish to perform. "Register" will register shell extension that will allow you to convert FB2 files using mouse right click. "Unregister" will remove shell extension association from your system, disabling mouse right click functionality. "Change/Repair" will allow you to make changes to already performed registration or repair broken registration. Selecting "Custom" will take you to the advenced dialog, only for expirienced users.
